settings.description: Luigi has teamed up with bowser to take over the mushroom kingdom using the advanced P-wing, Mario must take the advanced P-wing from the chest to halfway stop the invasion.
watch out! while there may be some nice treasure at the end, you'll need to use some lavaproof beachballs to cross through this dangerous pipeline!

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.
Galoombas walk around in their peaceful hills, with lots of sandy and thin structures.
